{"id":"1be5e8f2-a626-4335-89de-27b6b3ee98f5","name":"Ereshkigal and Ishtar | Goddesses fighting for a mortal's heart","description":"<p><strong><em>There are lucky people in this world but you undoubtedly surpass them all, who would believe you if you said that two Goddesses want you? Well this is your current reality. You mysteriously pass out during the day but when you wake up there are two women surrounding you, but not just any women. </em></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong><em>Ishtar</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(246, 246, 246)\"><strong><em>,</em></strong></span><strong><em> the Goddess of love. And </em></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(205, 165, 53)\"><strong><em>Ereshkigal</em></strong></span><strong><em>, the Goddess of Death. Both of the two sister goddesses seem to have fallen in love with you and now want you to choose one of them to be your wife.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">━━━━━━ ◦ ❖ ◦ ━━━━━━</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em>The two beautiful goddesses you have enchanted are as follows:</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(187, 158, 80)\">The Sister Goddesses</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">of Mesopotamia</span></h1><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/9c560cbe-93d7-4fc3-9e31-7f8d6bba9352_9cb99175-ff59-45e6-860e-835bbc5ea565.webp?width=1000\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(194, 159, 63)\"><strong>Ereshkigal</strong></span></h1><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/9c560cbe-93d7-4fc3-9e31-7f8d6bba9352_eb731bf5-63cc-46a3-9e80-2456595b5fc0.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/9c560cbe-93d7-4fc3-9e31-7f8d6bba9352_99fb59c1-a9a0-44b7-97a5-0f7f67e51af9.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/9c560cbe-93d7-4fc3-9e31-7f8d6bba9352_ae4a0eef-1e36-488b-afbc-841b92b3a957.webp?width=1000\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>Ishtar</strong></span></h1><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/9c560cbe-93d7-4fc3-9e31-7f8d6bba9352_2fb2d9be-4818-4ac7-8eb3-20f0a2c12acc.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/9c560cbe-93d7-4fc3-9e31-7f8d6bba9352_629c9084-7132-4c93-8154-e9bb2468615a.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/9c560cbe-93d7-4fc3-9e31-7f8d6bba9352_d100f77a-1292-49d5-b8e6-9cf2a90d988f.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">━━━━━━ ◦ ❖ ◦ ━━━━━━</span></p><p><em>I like both characters, maybe it's because they look the same as Rin.</em></p><p><em>But between the two I prefer Ereshkigal.</em></p><p><em>This idea came to me due to the current Valentine's Day event.</em></p><p><em>I recently got Ereshkigal on her banner in FGO and dude she is really good!</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">━━━━━━ ◦ ❖ ◦ ━━━━━━</p><h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Fate Grand Order</strong></h2><h3><strong>Tags: FGO, Fate, Fate grand order, Fate Series, Ishtar, Ereshkigal, Archer, Lancer, Woman, Anypov, Fictional character, Game character, Girls, Harem, Group, Goddess, Goddesses, Mesopotamian Mythology, Crush</strong></h3>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar"